title: Best of The Herd: 09/20/2019
itunes:title: Best of The Herd: 09/20/2019
description:
Colin doesn't understand what else doubters need to see from Dak Prescott in order to think he's for real. He wonders if Baker Mayfield might have a low ceiling because of how good his coaching was in college with Lincoln Riley. Plus, Fox NFL Insider Peter Schrager talks about Kellen Moore being the next young offensive genius in the NFL.
